Package csheets.ext.test.ui

Provides specialized JTable components for displaying and providing editing of test cases and test case parameters.

ValidationStateRenderer A combo box in which validation states are selected, which acts as a table cell renderer.
 

Package csheets.ext.test.ui Description

Provides specialized JTable components for displaying and providing editing of test cases and test case parameters. Also provides some UI components for visualization.
